# Vite production bundle for the React islands. Generated locally by
# `npm run build` and at deploy-time by CI; tracking it pollutes the
# branch with ~50 hashed asset files (~1.8 MB) per rebuild and was
# causing the auto-snapshot hook to push a fresh dist on every commit.
# Deploys MUST run `npm run build` before serving — see README §deploy.
